results.title: Riddick

results.description:
So Our Vinbook video went viral...

Naturally, I became self-conscious... and thought maybe I shouldn't have exposed myself like that...

Then I had dinner with my dad, and surprisingly... he said he loved it... and thought it was deep on a few levels...

The Studio called today... and asked if I would be interested in doing a Musical...

Hmmm...

P.s. Don't be afraid to step out of your comfort zone, you don't have to be perfect... just believe in yourself.

You inspire me...

/smile

P.s. Thanks for the love...
Happy V Day...

Because of your excitement about the Super Bowl's FF6 trailer, the studio wanted me to show you the first 30 seconds of tomorrow's Extended First Look...

Tuesday 9am pst!

P.s. Your voice, your passion, has truly driven this saga...

Thanks for the love.

results.description:
My mother always encouraged us to be inventive... as an alternative to spending money for presents.

Creativity runs deeper than gifts one could buy in a store.

She also said the most important thing to do for the holidays is to write someone's name... just writing someone's name makes a person feel noticed and is more important than the actual gift.

P.s. My Grandmother would play this song every Christmas... and I would always sing along... haha...

This one's for Grandma...
